#: src/getbar.c:883
msgid ""
"Usage: getbar [OPTION]... URL\n"
"Download URL with HTTP(S) GET and record throughput bars.\n"
msgstr ""
"Cach dung: getbar [TUY-CHON]... URL\n"
"Tai URL bang HTTP(S) GET va ghi lai chuoi cot throughput.\n"

#: src/getbar.c:888
msgid "split by received block size\n"
msgstr "chia theo kich thuoc khoi nhan\n"

#: src/getbar.c:890
msgid "split by time interval (NUM may be fractional)\n"
msgstr "chia theo khoang thoi gian (NUM co the la so thap phan)\n"

#: src/getbar.c:892
msgid "stop after receiving NUM bytes\n"
msgstr "dung sau khi nhan NUM byte\n"

#: src/getbar.c:894
msgid "stop after timeout\n"
msgstr "dung khi het thoi gian\n"

#: src/getbar.c:896
msgid "output offset and polynomial coeffs\n"
msgstr "xuat offset va he so da thuc\n"

#: src/getbar.c:898
msgid "render chart (.png/.svg/.pdf/.eps) or save script\n"
msgstr "ve bieu do (.png/.svg/.pdf/.eps) hoac luu script\n"

#: src/getbar.c:900
msgid "overwrite gnuplot output file\n"
msgstr "ghi de tep dau ra gnuplot\n"

#: src/getbar.c:902
msgid "output estimated bytes/sec after delay\n"
msgstr "xuat byte/giay uoc tinh sau do tre\n"

#: src/getbar.c:904
msgid "print summary after series: count size duration bps\n"
msgstr "in tom tat sau chuoi: so luong kich thuoc thoi luong bps\n"

#: src/getbar.c:906
msgid "omit pre-data wait from series, window, count; set -p offset\n"
msgstr "bo thoi gian cho truoc du lieu khoi chuoi, cua so, dem; dat offset -p\n"

#: src/getbar.c:908
msgid "more logging to stderr\n"
msgstr "ghi them nhat ky ra stderr\n"

#: src/getbar.c:910
msgid "omit the bar series on stdout\n"
msgstr "bo qua chuoi cot tren stdout\n"

#: src/getbar.c:912
msgid "display this help and exit\n"
msgstr "hiển thị trợ giúp này và thoát\n"

#: src/getbar.c:914
msgid "output version information and exit\n"
msgstr "in thông tin phiên bản và thoát\n"

#: src/getbar.c:916
msgid ""
"Block mode (-b) prints per-block durations in microseconds. By default\n"
"the first value is the wait before data arrives. With -d that wait is\n"
"omitted from the series and derived metrics; -p then reports the delay\n"
"as offset. Interval mode (-i) includes leading zero intervals by default;\n"
"with -d they are omitted and -p offset is the idle time in seconds.\n"
"Polynomial, count, and estimate lines are printed after the series.\n"
"Optional theming: $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/getbar/gnuplot.rc\n"
msgstr ""
"Che do khoi (-b) in thoi luong moi khoi bang micro giay. Mac dinh gia tri dau la thoi gian cho truoc khi du lieu den; voi -d thoi gian cho do bi loai khoi chuoi va cac chi so phu thuoc; -p bao cao do tre lam offset. Che do khoang thoi gian (-i) mac dinh bao gom cac khoang zero dau; voi -d chung bi loai bo va offset -p la thoi gian nghi tinh bang giay.\n"
"Cac dong da thuc, dem va uoc luong duoc in sau chuoi.\n"
"Tuy chon giao dien: $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/getbar/gnuplot.rc\n"

#: src/getbar.c:924
#, c-format
msgid "Report bugs to: <%s>\n"
msgstr "Báo lỗi tới: <%s>\n"

